Interface Revisions.Factory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectRevisionsFactory
    Enclosing class:
    Revisions
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Revisions.Factory
    If you supply an instance of Revisions.Factory to a Model via Model#Model(Factory, Type...) etc. the model takes care, that create(Context) is called only while the model is connected and only once for each connect.
